
July 13, 2016

  This is what I get when I run sys:get_status for an FSM

3> sys:get_status(a).
{status,<0.40.0>,
        {module,gen_fsm},
        [[{'$ancestors',[a_sup,<0.38.0>]},
          {'$initial_call',{a,init,1}}],
         running,<0.39.0>,[],
         [{header,"Status for state machine a"},
          {data,[{"Status",running},
                 {"Parent",<0.39.0>},
                 {"Logged events",[]},
                 {"StateName",state_name}]},
          {data,[{"StateData",{state,1,"1",<<"1">>}}]}]]}
